These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, mirinda, iced-tea, cola
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, animation, disaster, mystery
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, nigerian, brazilian, pakistani, russian
5 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, dog, fish, frog
 1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is the person drinking mirinda##1
 5. the owner of the goat is the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the argentine is on the left of the brazilian##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the person drinking cola is between the nigerian and the person watching mystery movies##2
12. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
13. the russian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | juice        | sprite | cola     | mirinda   | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | animation     | adventure      | disaster | mystery   | scientific    |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | nigerian     | argentine | brazilian | russian  |
| Pet           | goldfish | dog      | frog     | fish   | goat     |

