.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, chess, traveling, cooking
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, punk, trance, indie
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, brazilian, pakistani, russian, argentine
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, ship, car, airplane, snowmobile
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the person driving the ship is between the mexican and the fan of indie##2
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 7. the fan of house is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 8. the pakistani is the fan of trance##1
 9. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
10. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the pakistani is the person who's hobby is chess##1
12. the person driving the ship is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | traveling | camping | cooking    | rock-climbing  | chess    |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | hip-hop       | punk      | house | trance        |
| Nationality   | argentine   | brazilian     | mexican    | russian  | pakistani     |
| Transport     | car    | ship | snowmobile | airplane | boat |

