.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, gardening, woodworking, sudoku, board-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, horror, spy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, funk, folk, dubstep
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, skiing, ice-hockey, climbing, rugby
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
13. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading | board-games     | woodworking   | gardening   | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | horror | crime | fantasy | spy        |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | hip-hop      | folk       | dubstep       | disco       |
| Sport         | skiing | rugby  | climbing    | golf    | ice-hockey        |

