.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There 5 different types of food: avocado, cucumber, nectarine, kale, lime
The people have 5 different hobbies: disco-climbing, camping, writing, collecting, fishing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, country, house, electronic, disco
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, polish, russian, french
 1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is disco-climbing is on the right of the fan of country##1
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the french is between the fan of electronic and the person eating kale##2
 5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 6. the fan of disco is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of disco is in the middle##1
10. the fan of electronic is the australian##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
12. the australian is on the right of the fan of house##1
13. the fan of country is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Food          | lime  | nectarine     | kale   | cucumber     | avocado |
| Hobby         | fishing | disco-climbing    | writing  | collecting | camping   |
| Music-Genre   | country        | techno    | disco     | house     | electronic    |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | polish | russian | french | australian   |

