.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, sprite, coffee, hot-chocolate
There 5 different types of food: radish, carrot, pepper, eggplant, grapes
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, analyst, doctor, project-manager, accountant
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, tennis, basketball, baseball, biathlon
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person eating radish##2
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the analyst##1
 8. the accountant is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
12. the project-manager is on the left of the scientist##1
13. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | coffee       | hot-chocolate       | 7up   | sprite      | tea    |
| Food       | grapes | eggplant        | radish       | pepper       | carrot |
| Job        | accountant     | analyst        | project-manager | scientist        | doctor  |
| Sport      | baseball | basketball | handball      | biathlon | tennis  |

