5 different pets are kept: frog, hedgehog, guinea-pig, lizard, turtle
The people use 5 different means of transport: scooter, van, jet-ski, car, trike
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the turtle is the person driving the van##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the australian##2
 5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1
 7. the german is on the right of the brazilian##1
 8. the italian is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is the german##1
10. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the brazilian##1
12. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess   | cooking | puzzles  | filmmaking | woodworking |
| Nationality   | brazilian | german     | australian   | nigerian     | italian      |
