 5. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the bus is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
12. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | tea       | sprite    | lemonade | hot-chocolate  | cola        |
| Hobby       | magic-tricks | hiking | skydiving  | singing | photography    |
| Sport       | lacrosse        | climbing   | badminton  | snowboarding   | baseball |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bus      | subway      | scooter | airplane  |

